308
00:22:24,241 --> 00:22:26,551
Huh? Um, yeah.

309
00:22:27,227 --> 00:22:30,539
- I'll eat with you.
- Oh, no! It's okay.

310
00:22:31,974 --> 00:22:35,310
Hey, how can I just leave after seeing you eat by yourself?

311
00:22:37,187 --> 00:22:40,031
Kang Seo Woo, You really are the nicest of them all.

312
00:22:40,031 --> 00:22:41,583
