Oh, really?

322
00:23:10,545 --> 00:23:15,091
Um, I was planning to marry the guy who'd let me eat both drumsticks.

323
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:20,180
Here. Have both of the drumsticks. I'll be generous.

324
00:23:20,180 --> 00:23:21,306
Wow!

325
00:23:22,149 --> 00:23:24,151
Thanks!

326
00:23:25,010 --> 00:23:27,654
Wow, this is so good!

327
00:23:27,654 --> 00:23:30,657
I wonder why it tastes so good? Wow!

328
00:23:43,337 --> 00:23:44,338
Yes, hello?

329
00:23:44,421 --> 00:23:47,925
When are you going to pay me for finding Kang Yeong Jin for you?

330
00:23:48,717 --> 00:23:51,687
Excuse me? What do you mean?

331
00:23:51,687 --> 00:23:54,348
I sent you a text before with his information!

332
00:23:54,348 --> 00:23:56,266
Were you not able to meet him?

333
00:23:56,266 --> 00:23:59,827
