468
00:34:30,042 --> 00:34:34,913
Me too! It's my birthday today, too!

469
00:34:34,947 --> 00:34:36,623
You too?

470
00:34:36,623 --> 00:34:41,453
We're twins, so we have the same birthday.

471
00:34:42,700 --> 00:34:45,700
♫  Even if you laugh louder ♫

472
00:34:45,707 --> 00:34:51,738
Sorry. I'll definitely get you a present on your next birthday. .

473
00:34:51,738 --> 00:34:55,658
I'll give you a present on every birthday! Okay?

474
00:34:55,658 --> 00:35:01,690
♫  Don't leave me anywhere alone anymore  ♫

475
00:35:01,690 --> 00:35:05,252
♫  I want to say I love you just you ♫

476
00:35:05,252 --> 00:35:07,854
It's already tomorrow.

477
00:35:24,688 --> 00:35:26,189
Where are you going?

478
00:35:27,457 --> 00:35:29,459
I have a lot of plans today.

479
00:36:00,616 --> 00:36:03,869
Did the Chairman tell you to keep an eye on me?

480
00:36:06,939 --> 00:36:08,882
I wonder what I did wrong.

481
00:36:10,359 --> 00:36:13,586
Why does he keep doubting me?

482
00:36:14,530 --> 00:36:17,040
I don't know why either.

483
00:36:19,827 --> 00:36:25,657
Do you think that I'm cheating on the Chairman, too?

484
00:36:25,657 --> 00:36:29,519
It's not my place to make that kind of judgment.

485
00:36:35,801 --> 00:36:38,970
We're here. You can get out.

486
00:36:42,140 --> 00:36:45,852
Can't we have a meal together?

487
00:36:49,831 --> 00:36:51,291
I'm sorry.

488
00:36:57,639 --> 00:37:02,844
I didn't have the right to have you buy me a meal with your first paycheck.

489
00:37:04,371 --> 00:37:08,391
But I really wanted to buy you a tie if you got a job somewhere.

490
00:37:09,877 --> 00:37:13,663
I know it's quite overdue, but will you accept it?

491
00:37:47,598 --> 00:37:49,533
Yes, hello.

492
00:37:49,533 --> 00:37:51,376
Please, take a seat.

493
00:37:55,547 --> 00:37:59,326
I'm trying to find a room.

494
00:37:59,326 --> 00:38:00,535
For rent?

495
00:38:00,535 --> 00:38:02,529
Um, yes.

496
00:38:02,529 --> 00:38:04,831
How much can you afford to pay in terms of a security deposit?

497
00:38:05,449 --> 00:38:08,627
Is there a place I can move into without paying a security deposit?

498
00:38:08,627 --> 00:38:14,249
Well, you'll have to look into basement rooms, or a student hostel.

499
00:38:14,666 --> 00:38:15,634
A... student hostel?

500
00:38:15,634 --> 00:38:18,128
It wouldn't be the best place for a young lady to live by herself, but...

501
00:38:18,128 --> 00:38:21,715
Oh, just a moment. Let me take a look here.

502
00:38:24,852 --> 00:38:26,720
Hope Student Hostel

503
00:38:29,056 --> 00:38:32,208
- Please give me a call, then.
- Yes, I will.

504
00:38:42,903 --> 00:38:44,254
Yeah?

505
00:38:44,254 --> 00:38:45,489
Where are you?

506
00:38:46,573 --> 00:38:49,776
Why do you care where I am?

507
00:38:49,826 --> 00:38:51,912
It's your birthday today.

508
00:38:52,746 --> 00:38:56,400
Yeah. So I'm meeting up with some friends today.

509
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:59,127
So can we hang up already?

510
00:39:24,152 --> 00:39:26,529
What a great age to be.

